    var operating_system = source.u_os_type.toString();


    //This if statement uses JavaScript regular expressions to search the operating system
    if ( operating_system.match(/linux/i) != null ){
        target.sys_class_name="cmdb_ci_linux_server";
    } else if ( operating_system.match(/win/i) != null ){
        target.sys_class_name="cmdb_ci_win_server";
    }
    
})(source, target, map, log, action==="update");
]]></script><source_table>u_cloudcenter_import_vms</source_table><sys_class_name>sys_transform_map</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-09-07 17:34:03</sys_created_on><sys_id>53a162750f01030015e609bce1050eca</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>CloudCenter Transform VMs</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_transform_map_53a162750f01030015e609bce1050eca</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2017-09-07 17:41:11</sys_updated_on><target_table>cmdb_ci_server</target_table></sys_transform_map></record_update>
